race.description: Zipping Kyrgios @ Stud Maiden Heat 4 H
race.comment: SPRING SIGNAL (1) has been freshened since being safely held on debut at Richmond over 320m (19.59). Has the inside box this time. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. WAVERLEY MISS (3) has her first outing without a trial but profiles nicely for this. Among the main hopes. MOTOR CITY VANCE (8) is a handily bred pup making his debut without a trial. Bold showing expected here. LUMEAH SPARKLES (5) placed last time out so worth considering.
